refactor: memoize TVShow component and add lazy loading

- Wrap TVShow component with memo() to prevent unnecessary re-renders
- Add lazy loading for HeroSection and MediaGrid components
- Add useMemo for tvShowsData array to prevent recalculation
- Add useCallback for handleRetry to stabilize function reference
- Add height hints to LazyWrapper components
- Add Suspense fallback with LoadingFallback for better UX
